Class SupportingFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • finalAutomation.SupportingFunctions

  • public class SupportingFunctions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains supporting methods that perform tasks like
    -Reading and writing (Excel and POI related)
    -Sending email
    -Taking screenshots
